{"name":"Weapon Training (FGT)","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf1/icons/items/weapons/dagger-swordbreaker.PNG","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf1.class-abilities.RzEzudurxQFirFoF"},"pf1":{},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.mqWzoYM7b5GOGmuv","hash":"f97e0677a58e2c3c5a0251348b95a0ae171f6ded"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, a fighter gains a +1 bonus on attack and damage rolls with all weapons he is proficient with. A fighter also adds this bonus to any combat maneuver checks that are made with weapons he is proficient with. This bonus also applies to the fighter’s Combat Maneuver Defense when defending against disarm, steal, and sunder attempts made against weapons he is wielding and proficient with. This bonus increases by +1 at 7th, 11th, and 15th level.</p><p><strong>Increase:</strong> +[[floor((@classes.fighterLegendary.level +1)/ 4) + (@classes.fighterLegendary.level &gt;= 19 ? -1 : 0)]]</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[{"_id":"tKnkNFTG","formula":"max(0, min(4, 1 + floor((@classes.fighterLegendary.level - 3) / 4)))","operator":"add","subTarget":"cmd","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":4}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"+[[max(0, min(4, 1 + floor((@classes.fighterLegendary.level - 3) / 4)))]] to Attack, Damage, CMB and CMD with weapons he is proficient with.","subTarget":"meleeWeapon"},{"text":"+[[max(0, min(4, 1 + floor((@classes.fighterLegendary.level - 3) / 4)))]] to Attack, Damage, CMB and CMD with weapons he is proficient with.","subTarget":"rangedWeapon"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionar